  <entry>
    <title>2023-数据库课设-环境搭建-jdk</title>
    <link href="/2023/06/19/2023-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E8%AF%BE%E8%AE%BE-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-jdk/"/>
    <url>/2023/06/19/2023-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E8%AF%BE%E8%AE%BE-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-jdk/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>运行 SpringBoot 的 java 代码, 我用的是 jdk-11 版本</p><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><figure class="highlight mipsasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mipsasm">sudo apt update<br>sudo apt <span class="hljs-keyword">install </span>openjdk<span class="hljs-number">-11</span>-<span class="hljs-keyword">jdk</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword"></span><span class="hljs-keyword">java </span>--version<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2023/06/19/2023-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E8%AF%BE%E8%AE%BE-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-jdk/java.png"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
